data.description: Price reduction and ready for you! You will find a winner in this Glen Heights beauty! Large living room, with wood-burning fireplace and ceiling fan, opens to kitchen and is great for entertaining. Roof 2019! HVAC replaced 2021! Updated  electric stove 3 years old. Refrigerator (2 years old) included if desired. Water heater is 3 years old. Gutters were added 3 years ago. Pantry cabinet was added to kitchen. Primary bath features a walk-in tub and separate shower. All three bedrooms feature walk-in closet. Ceiling fan in primary bedroom. Front entry two-car garage. Exclude cabinets in garage. This home has been loved, and the big updates have been done! Convenient access to Interstate 35S. One hour notice and one hour window for showings. Come and enjoy a beautiful home! This home conveys a welcoming vibe! 2023-11-28
